name: MADISON GORDON
description:
MADISON GORDON its a Australian twitch streamer.

First of all, I would like to thank JernauGurgeh for encouraging me to try my first Textual inversion as a result of his brilliant works already published and his little guide.

To train this IT I have used a dataset of 32 images. 300 steps were enough for an optimal result.

Embedding weight works well between 0.98 and 1.

I hope you enjoy it and I can learn more for the future with the feedback :D
